If you wish to use this open source project please keep the links to previous coders.

How to use:
1) Upload data to ur website.
2) Run mysql file in mysql db
3) Edit /include/requiredFuntions.php set the varibles mysql login/password , bitocind login/password , Domain name
4) setup cronjobs to run every 10 mins and payout for hourly (or your choice)
5) go into database edit settings to match your site info.
6) i think thats it. have fun.

